         <div type="translation">
            <ab>Horeion to his father Apollonios, greeting. Receive by letter 908 silver drachmae that I sent with a lodger (tenant?).;Send me the medicine chest and ask the doctor for the bitter medicine and the other sweeter one.;I pray that you are well.</ab>
